  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Quantity Surveyor",
  "description": "<p>Join Our Team: Quantity Surveyor</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>We're seeking an experienced Quantity Surveyor to join our dynamic team! As a key member of our project team, you'll play a crucial role in managing project costs and ensuring successful project delivery.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Your Responsibilities:</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>- Conduct take-off quantities and prepare pricing comparisons</p>\n<p>- Source and compare quotations from suppliers and subcontractors</p>\n<p>- Prepare project costings, contracts, and tender documents</p>\n<p>- Conduct site measurements and monitor subcontractor progress</p>\n<p>- Process progress payments, variation orders, and final accounts</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>What We're Looking For:</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>- Degree or Diploma in Quantity Surveying, Building, or equivalent</p>\n<p>- Minimum 3 years of experience in a Quantity Surveyor role (8+ years for Senior role)</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>What to Include in Your Application:</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>- Current and expected salary</p>\n<p>- Reason(s) for leaving your current role</p>\n<p>- Date of availability</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Only Shortlisted will be notified.</p>",
